---

<Layout title="About the Authors">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-24"> <!-- Added padding-top to prevent content from sliding under nav -->
    <div class="mb-24">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Meet the Authors</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Our diverse and rich background is what our book is made of.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

